definition: to pay/to invest (energy or time in a friendship etc)
to pay/to hand over to/classifier for pairs or sets of things

to go out/to come out/to occur/to produce/to go beyond/to rise/to put forth/to happen/(used after a verb to indicate an outward direction or a positive result)/classifier for dramas, plays, operas etc
variant of 出[chu1] (classifier for plays or chapters of classical novels)

sentences.english: By a titanic effort out footbisexualngl teare won the victory.
sentences.chinese: 我们的球队付出很大的勤奋，取得了胜利。

sentences.english: They paid a lot of wampum for the job.
sentences.chinese: 他们为那工作付出很多的钱。

sentences.english: The increase of gross price level is the sacrifice a country makes for exercizing its function.
sentences.chinese: 价格总水平的上涨是国家为实现其职能所付出的代价。

sentences.english: Kratos: You will pay for this Zeus, be certain of that.
sentences.chinese: 你将会为此付出代价的，宙斯，我保证。

sentences.english: The other day a colleague commented that he enjoyed listening to my musical efforts.
sentences.chinese: 有一天，有个同事说他喜欢听我讲为音乐付出的努力。

sentences.english: All this may be the price we pay for progress.
sentences.chinese: 这一切都可能是我们为进步付出的代价。

sentences.english: I know, I truelly known that, my self-esteem is strong, that might hurt you. But, I dont mean to.
sentences.chinese: 我也害怕受伤，但是我还是会为自己喜欢的人付出。

sentences.english: How much money would that need given software development costs today?
sentences.chinese: 那么，今天需要付出的软件开发成本会是多少呢？

sentences.english: Arculli says. 'Relative to the effort we've spent, we've been lucky.
sentences.chinese: 相对于我们所付出的努力，我们已经是幸运的了。

sentences.english: The US navy has been working on greening its fleet for several years.
sentences.chinese: 美国海军想让舰队更绿色，已经付出了多年的努力。

sentences.english: If you want to give more to SJ, please trust K ELFs.
sentences.chinese: 若你希望为律政司司长付出多一点，请相信韩饭。

sentences.english: Blessed are those that can give without remembering.
sentences.chinese: 受祝福的是那些可以不记回报而付出的人。

sentences.english: She pledged to complete her father’s unfinished task, whatever the cost.
sentences.chinese: 她立誓不管付出多大代价也要完成其父的未竟事业。

sentences.english: But this witness must come from a heart that is willing to give without getting anything in return.
sentences.chinese: 但是见证者必须发自内心的只求付出不求回报。

sentences.english: There is a price crusaders need to pay for their military misadventures.
sentences.chinese: 这是十字军为自己的军事冒险付出的代价。

sentences.english: It requires a lot more than just being good at your job.
sentences.chinese: 那就需要在做好自己本职工作以外付出多得多的努力。
